data.description: Welcome to the gated community of Las Brisas II. Las Brisas II is a boutique 55+ gated community with low HOAs and centrally located. This home offers two bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a formal dinning and living room, and 3 car garage. The kitchen opens up to the family/ great room and offers an eat-in dinning area as well. The primary bedroom is spacious and has an office/ den/ seating area/ room located just off the bedroom. Primary bathroom has a Safe Step walk-in tub/ shower combo, double vanity, and spacious walk-in closet. Secondary bedroom is on the other end of the hall for maximum privacy for visitors and has direct access to the secondary bathroom with a walk-in in shower. Back yard has been upgraded with turf, a putting green, covered patio, and has a spot for your RV, with RV hookups - such a great benefit. Exterior of home has been recently painted. PLEASE NOTE - Photos on listing have had the paint adjusted to match the rest of the house. Seller is working on paint quotes and will have the home painted all one color.
